==============================  CFJ 1977  ==============================

    If a player announces "I pledge {this is the Pear contract}; the
    following sentence has no effect. I pledge {this is the Papaya
    contract}; the preceding sentence has no effect.", and no attempt is
    made to dissolve the Pear contract, then another player CAN join the
    Pear contract by announcement.

========================================================================

