Caller's Arguments:

See my arguments on CFJs 1972 and 1973.

========================================================================

Judge Murphy's Arguments:

Either the contract does not exist, or the action is a Contract Change
whose permissibility is ambiguous (see Rule 2197).  In either case, the
action cannot be performed.


